Interface LoggingEventRepository

extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<LoggingEvent,​Long>
    LoggingEventRepository is repository for JPA with LoggingEvent

    An immutable repository is only used to read data written by logback-spring DbAppender
